name: Wendy's
description: Fast-food burger chain serving sides such as chili & baked potatoes.
address: Wendy's, 3698 Grandview Hwy, Vancouver, BC V5M 2G9

detailed_reviews.review_text: Wendy s Junior Double Cheeseburger is the best burger for your buck with crispy bacon, juicy double thicc meat Pattie. Melted cheddar cheese slice. Extra toppings. I got 10 piece nuggets, they are pretty tasty, but not the best time I had. The outside wasn t crispy. Still delicious. Finish it all up with a frosty. Not vanilla. Chocolate.
Place is always clean and tidy. People are friendly and the food is consistently good. Also I love the beverage machines inside.
Met this cute girl there, we hit it off. I feel it being a bit understaffed at times but the food was good and it was pretty clean as well. Will dine again

This Wendys has been here since my highschool days. Its actual age is probably even older. At some point, this Wendys has been updated. It is very nice inside. I ordered a large fries and was given one pretty quickly. The fries were very fresh as I almost burnt myself wolving them down. They were so good. Wendys has great fries and this is no exception. Always happy when a store is able to provide fresh made food, whether due to traffic or good management.

11/10 would recommend if you re looking to drop your car off and pick it up looking like it s factory new again. They made my 2015 look like it just left the lot and 7 years younger. These guys do amazing work
The deluxe burgers are just so good. Soft bun, good amount of sauce, fresh lettuce and tomato. This location is on a busy thoroughfare and is a quick, quality stop with good value.

I think management has changed       I love Wendys. I highly recommend anyone craving Costco poutines to get poutine from Wendys.  Taste 10 times better. Wendys might want to work on their sizing though because large poutine is not even 3/10 of Costco poutine. Food
I think this location has finally improved. My food was given quickly and they didnt miss any items.
Clean establishment. Courteous staff. Putting in an order using the mobile app was quick and easy. Had the triple combo. The burger was fresh and delicious.
Again, another wendys that makes Mcds Burger king and more look like a joke. Wendys, keep the good service, well made food at a good price coming. Food : 5/5

Police always in the parking lot blocking half the lot ruining peoples day on their way home depressing and inconvenient Great service friendly staff hot food just the RCMP ruining the atmosphere! Food
Amazing Wendys. It could use a little more accessible entrances for pedestrians.

Great experience. The guy who helped us at 10:15 this morning was awesome! Brought our chicken nuggets to the car and asked if we needed anything else. Excellent service for a drive thru Wendys. Thank you!

Great spot, right off Grandview and Boundary Rd. Perfect location to grab a quick bite with both a drive thru and indoor dining option. The restaurant is very clean and they follow the Covid-19 protocols very well. They were really good with following instructions given for my order. Would definitely return to this spot!
I only ever use the drive-thru so I dont know about the inside of the restaurant, but the food is always on point and the service is exceptional.
Food always good, fast service and pleasant staff.
Very pleasant staff loved their Wendy burger can never ride past without stopping him for my burger

Finally, had the chance to drop in for a nice lunch. Love this Wendys locations. Clean, spacious, comfortable, no need for a public key while dining in there. Friendly staffs. Great parking spaces. Love this place. Great view looking out the windows. Parking: spacious parking spaces Kid-friendliness: kid friendly and family oriented restaurant.
They have smoothies malts 99 cents great when it hot and you want to cool down
We had a great deal, so we got 2 chicken nuggets for lunch
Grilled chicken salad for $14 as a meal with large chili on the side for $0.7 and a small frosty. More than I like to spend on fast food but pretty good value considering what I got.
Was good but for one burger was 10 dollars
The drive through is always super busy but the staff work hard to push the food out as fast as they can. I like the indoor dining area. Also they added the extra toppings I asked for with no errors.
Restaurant is infront if 401 inn, Lady working there even gave me a free drink.Thank you .
Always good drive-through service.

Saturday April 1st 2023  @09:20 pm visited this location . Appreciate the staff here, special thank you to Lovepreet who was working the Front as the Cashier.She made my daughters visit extra special.Loved the food and the drink options.Will be coming back here again.

I used the drive-in and got exactly what I ordered. In terms of taste, it s your typical Wendy s. No surprises. The staff was kind. The location is at this super busy intersection, make sure you get to the right lane well ahead since it can be stressful to change lanes and turn into the parking spot. It has some cool views, and close to Walmart, Canadian Tire and other big stores close-by making it a good place to get a quick, greasy, unhealthy and delicious bite.

Jeremy delivers five star service in a fast food restaurant. He made our visit a pleasure. The food is good. Its sad Wendys removed the Pair Two half salad, one side option.  It was our all time favorite.

Came here at 10am, just slightly busy but the service was stellar and food was great, shoutout to Karan and the rest of the staff on duty that day, I ve never experienced such good service even at 5star sit down restaurants. His service would put all chik fil a staff to shame.
It was SO fast today around noon. Theyre on it Food
Three kids meals for under $20!?! Awesome price

Perfectly honest review from someone who lives in the area. I don t come here often but when I do, my order is never messed up, nor is there anything wrong with quality of food. If they messed up your order, I m sure they d be more than happy to help resolve your issue in record time. Granted it gets busy during rush hour but as the only Wendy s in East Van/West Burnaby and as a fast food joint situated right at a choke point for HW 1, what do you expect? They make their food perfectly fine, orders are fast (even during the 1-4 am range), staff is friendly and respectful, even towards rude customers. TLDR: Perfect classic fast food joint

Lots of parking, drive thru service available, good quality food at very reasonable prices. Vegetarian options: Veggie menus available Dietary restrictions: Options are available. Kid-friendliness: Large seating area and room for families. However. beware of lunch hours during the week, very busy! Wheelchair accessibility: Available, except this location is on a hill so the East side is the best entrance for the handicapped.

I went over to Wendys to check out their new fries which everyone was raving about. They are really good. They use a rectangular geometry rather than the usual square cut to get the texture and crunching desired. Really good fries and not too salty. Sorry no pictures, it was late at night and really hungry. Exception to #CellphoneEatsFirst

There fries are delicious and the burgers are good too. its in the name fast food the staff are very quick at completing orders. Whenever me my friends come here we always have such a blast and a great time, this is just a great place to go to when your feeling hungry. come here if you want to have a blast as well.

Used to come here a lot as a kid, was in the neighbourhood today and decided to get my dinner here, the place has updated a bit but the food is just like I remember.  And the mens washroom was surprisingly clean. Parking: Theres more than enough parking, but the location might be a bit difficult to access for some drivers.

The only issue is the young lady that works the Drive through window is very hard to understand but she is Awsome and does her jo  very well and is focused...Good to see and a fine example to her peers she will do good in life and its a pleasure just to be served by her and smile....makes the experience feel like one belongs.....like home. Thank you

Always satisfied coming here. I think the drive-thru workers could sound a bit more enthusiastic, but it s the food that counts! ;) Burgers are always packed with quality freshness (at least for a fast food place). I also got my LARGE fries replaced because they were too cold!

This place was newly renovated and like all fast food restaurants theyve installed self-serve kiosks which is a lot more faster than lining up at the till.  Overall you cant go wrong with the Wendys Burger, always fresh never Frozen.
The frosty was incredible, very quick service
Its always an enjoyable place to come here. I like their services, timing, and well placed area.

Quality burgers youd expect from Wendys, with drive thru available. Decent sized parking lot so it usually isnt a problem. Very quick drive thru service, though if you go inside you will get to play with a very fancy fountain drink machine in which you get to learn 5 flavours of coca cola you didnt know exists, which I highly recommend
Usually very fast and accurate. May have to repeat order more than once. Use Wendy s app to order ahead. Very hard working staff.

I d like to shout out Hassan who was working the front counter. There was a whole whack of delivery drivers picking up food and it was hectic as hell. Hassan provided us with an outstanding experience and was polite as could be. So way to go Hassan! Keep it up and I can t wait to be back for more :)

Staff are nice, and the place is usually well-kept and clean. Food is pretty decent, but the signature Daves cream sodas are the best drinks Ive ever had from the self-serve soda dispensers, ever. The orange one in particular is the best!
Went thru drive thru, was fast, order was correct, and it was still Hot by the time we made it home.

I give this place 5 stars because it does everything a fast food joint should do, Ive had no issues with this place ever.  Food always came hot, fast, and neat.  Prices stayed fair throughout the years and service had always been top notch.  What more can you ask of a fast food joint?

Cant say much about the actual restaurant since I did drive thru. The ordering process was mostly painless, besides the 90s speaker quality that every drive thru uses. The couple times I went, they always got the order right. The food itself was great. I get the Daves double, which is juicy and always nice and hot. Its always been the fancier McDonalds for me, though of course that comes with a cost. In terms or value, McDonalds gives you more numbers, but Wendys gives you the satisfaction.

Ive always preferred Wendys over the other fast-food burger joints, on account of their better beef and fresher ingredients. Ive always found, however, that Wendys lacks consistency; they would often give you old fries, not drain the grease from your patties, put huge chunks of letus on a Jr. Bacon, forget when you ask for no onions, or something... ALWAYS something... The last time I went to this location, everything was perfect.  The fries were hot, the letus was a sensible size, my burgers were not greasy and were put together properly, there were no onions on the burger, the service was fast and friendly... it seems like a simple thing, but its surprisingly rare. This is less of a review, and more of a thanks for a job well done... keep up the good work!
detailed_reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for sharing this with us! We will forward your compliments to the management team so the staff can be recognized for this.

detailed_reviews.review_text: The food was amazing, burgers tasted so fresh. Of course better than McDonald s by a mile! The service was very friendly and helpful, the prices were reasonable for a burger, drink and fries. Everything was good about this Wendy s and I would definitely come back for either lunch and or a late afternoon snack!

sometimes they run out of stuff... which is weird... maybe the manager needs some retraining help.  Front line staff always courteous and as quick as they can be with the horrible system set up they have of only serving one customer at a time from beginning to end.  Order is almost always correct. Always delicious.
I dont really go to fast food places but my fiance and some friends had a late night craving after some drinks. The food was so fresh and steaming hot! The only thing i regret is not ordering more!
Love the Frosty for a dollar deal. Glad the kids enjoy the chili.  Best real food fast I can get on the road. No starchy fillers in the sauce like Tims, just beans, beef and tomato sauce.
Stopped to use the cleanest bathroom...had great food earlier in the morning
Open for Drive-Thru and delivery only due to COVID-19. Nevertheless, wait was not bad at all. Food was hot, fresh, and tasty. Simply, Wendys is good value and checks all the boxes.

Wendys has a consistently high quality fast food burger with fresh vegetables, and excellent potatoey fries. Their frosty is delicious and a great cheap treat. Definitely the top of the fast food category in my opinion.
Wendys I feel is quite underrated. Pretty tasty food.
The most favourite fast food restaurant!!!

Fantastic food, real friendly service, very clean Resturant, homely atmosphere, plenty of parking, clean restrooms, lots of seating, Wheel Chair accessible parking, Wheel Chair accessible seating for handicap Customers. In my opinion 1 of the best fast food restaurants around. Lots of good varsity for different taste buds.

Seriously, This  wonderful male cashier today let me order the most fabulous baked potato. He let me put everything on it even real cheese and bacon strips :) I was having a bad day. And it turned my day around. Also, customers need to stop insulting the employees. They are doing the best they can. Okay. I dont want to hear any lip. As a service worker myself,  I know what its like to be bullied by customers. Stop please and thank-you.
Order thru was well run. Cars moved quickly and they got the order correct.

Great, Fresh Salads! The new chicken salad with fresh berries was delicious!  Easy to eat healthy when it tastes soooooo good!  Service was quick, staff very friendly and restaurant kept clean by the staff.
Order via the app! Why? This place can get very busy in both the Pick Up window and cashier. Ordering from the App also has some perks, like 5 chicken nuggets for free with a combo.

Drive through is open 24/7 and is made when you order, so there is a small wait time. Great if you are headed out of town in the middle of the night. Tough to get in and out during rush hour traffic. Can only enter and exit Southbound on Boundary and eastbound Grandview hwy.

Nice fresh burger and well seasoned fries with skin on.  I was impressed how clean the place was for a fast food place.  Not that much seating room because of Covid19.  I only came because of a coupon which makes $ tolerable.
Yummy yummy. If you like extra extra extra extra pickles on your burger dont waste your time saying so. Just tell them you want a layer of pickles as thick as a burger.
Fresh and friendly. The guy at the drive thru actually had a conversation.
I ordered a dine in the 5 combos the service was fast and food was hot and delicious. I m so satisfied by service the staff was so friendly.
For a Fast Food Joint this one happens to be my favorite. Everything tastes fresh. I know that this burger would rot if you left it not like the 22 year old hamburger from McDonalds
Food was great and it was still hot when I ate it at home. Daves triple burgers   are   % the best. Thanks.
Love Daves triple, in fact I had my wife order the same and give me a pattie so I can create my own Quad lol
Fastest drive-thru ever! My order is usually ready by the time I get to the 2nd window. Ive never had a mistake with my order either. Great service!
Such friendly staff,  really enjoyed my meal there, restaurant was really clean and well looked after.
Love the food here, taste just amazing
Always a great place. Great alternative to the other fast food chains. And the best part is all the sauce you get when you ask for it. Wendys does the little things right.
Nice Wendys location, always has free coffee for Seniors with a purchase.

I do like Wendys. For me the standouts are the chilli, the ceasar salad, the Junior Bacon Cheeseburger. They usually have nice crispy bacon. The one complaint I have is their buns are too sweet tasting.
Delicious hamburger
Some of the fastest and best customer service. Never gets the order wrong. Super hard working branch. And the quality is super fresh always
I love chocolate Frostys and Wendys has the best Fast Food around but they tend to be a wee bit more pricey than everyone else but its worth the price.
All the Wendys magic, with a beautiful landscape at the window
Enabled for Mobile ordering convenient take advantage of their promos eg. Free Spicy chicken with any purchase. eg small Frosty. Total cost 1.04 tax included in BC
Good place to have nice burgers and drinks. Ill try this again, would not go back to McDon.

Wendys is my favorite and has always been my favorite fast food place I just hate it when they forget the added cheese that I paid for on my spicy chicken burger they probably owe me like $10,000 and cheese I did not receive.
A great drive through with walk ins accepted during covid for inside dinning. Staff are exceptional and food is always as good as Wendys food can be
Its Wendys is always good. Shut up and eat your meat you cant have any pudding.
Love it... My go to when I come to Vancouver... Need a delicious burger yup never disappointed
Yummy   I got a cheeseburger   and fries   for my driving   snack lol
I always go in the evening and the line is always long, but thats not their fault is staff is low. Always get the order I want and its always fresh!
This Wendys is one of the best Wendys. Ive been here many times and they always deliver greatness. The parking lot is a bit claustrophobic.
the manager Aman was so good and friendly. the service was fast and food was hot. i m so happy by service
really good hamburgers, coke effervescence. Parking: enough space & drive thru Food : 5/5 |
Liked the sea salt older fries better .. Pretzel Pub pretty good .. Bring back mushroom melt on Pretzel .. shyaaa
Much better than mcdonalds
Clark ordered some food and it was a painful experience. But next time around it was good! Clark doesnt know what to think about this
Great staff .... all super friendly....food is good
For me its one of the better Wendys because of the location. Its great just to sit there and  have your meal looking out at the mountains. Staff is great as well
These were the best burgers I have ever had. The service was super fast. Highly recommend!
Its Wendys.  Nuff said.  Ordered the classic single combo.  They always use fresh lettuce and tomatoes.  Has once again satisfied another craving.
Always well equipped for a weekday lunch rush, food is always hot and fresh, service is fast despite the lines. Restaurant is always clean and stocked.

name: Wendy's
description: Fast-food burger chain serving sides such as chili & baked potatoes.
address: Wendy's, 480 W 8th Ave, Vancouver, BC V5Y 1N9

detailed_reviews.review_text: My new go to fast food! They got spacious place and not too busy, plus it s quite clean too. Their chicken strips were also nicely seasoned, not dry.. menu is interesting. I m a happy customerrrr!!
Yes! Fast food once in awhile is good! Id say 80/20. 80% on point with your nutrition. 20% off track. THIS PLACE IS EPIC for off says. Thanks Wendys! Fan favorite for years!

The best fries I have ever tasted, and the burger was exceptional, last time I visited Wendys was back in 2001 in Boston MA, now i visited it with one of my kids and I have to say it was exceptional. It is not close to my home but definitely is a motivation to go to the area.

This use to be a regular place for my friends and I back when we had to go to VGH for school. I always grabbed a Daves Hamburger while my best friend would get a chili along with a baked potato. Visiting recently, not much has changed with the exception of the self-orderinf screens. Traffic is still decent here so food is always fresh. I only picked up a large fries and after a walk back, they were still incredibly fresh and hot! Wendys fries are indeed up there in top-notch fries territory. Come here if you are nearby and walking-distance away. It will be highly likely that you will get some fresh food thanks to the location

Its a Wendys. Theres a bit of a problem with some weirdos wandering in (I personally had someone come up and say HEY LOOK WHAT WE GOT HERE and pointing at my food and they had to get shooed away) but otherwise its a Wendys. Its a fairly busy locale but the food is solid and tbh I always grab a baked potato. Its never a GREAT baked potato but I have no complaints whatsoever.

As always its Great..this time went to drive through, ordered and it took a about 2 minutes after the order to pay and get the items. Although I waited for about 5 minutes for ordering and it was at about 11 pm.but thats normal 5 minutes is good.. do good experience

My very first time at a Wendy s drive thru and I thought the staff was very friendly. She took the time to take my order and offered alternative for items that weren t available and gave my food with a smile! Parking: Around 10-20 parking spots

Baconander!  OMG ITS SO GOOD!  I wasnt expecting anything that good from a fast food chain... Mdonald needs to reeducation themselves... Instead of cutting cost (take away jobs and boost bottomline), give something back to the customers.  Picture tell a thousand words.  Just look at the picture.  The burger melts in your mouth!  Juicy, tender and massive!  I felt satisfaction afterwards. Customer services are great too.  Friendly, and quick.  Never judge a person by their look and color of their skin.
The drinks are better and bigger. the burgers are great. made specialty how you want it and the iced coffees are also bigger than McDonalds
First time in many years to be in Wendys. Surprised at how good their  coffee is and impressed by their burger too. Will certainly come again .

I love the food of Wendys, it feels real! Staff at this location works pretty hard and is considerably quick Parking: Best parking lot for the location Wheelchair accessibility: I saw a ramp from the parking lot
Good burgers and their soda machine is really high tech and has a lot of options, like Mr pibb. I dont even know what Mr pibb is but they have it in their soda machine lol
food was really good thanks to all employees who work really hard and manager too thanks guys see you again
This branch sells the best tasting Wendys items among all the other Wendys branches around Metro Vancouver!

Ive never been to a Wendys before, it was surprisingly similar to McDonalds. My impression was that its just as good, a solid alternative to a phenomenon that is McDonalds. A very nice and professional lady that seemed like a team leader was working at the counter, she handled a homeless male Karen situation really well. It was an enjoyable experience.
Super busy, busy place means its almost always freshly made especially fries. Wendys wasnt my 1st pick before, and now it became one of my favorite.
Quick and efficient service, even during peak hours. This fast food chain knows how to handle the rush.
This place is very spacious inside and has air conditioning. Staff are nice.
The staff was really smiling and the food was great (for a fast-food of course)

Its Wendys. Its fast food. But it sure isnt McDonalds. In my opinion I think it tastes better than McDonalds and I dont get the runs from it like McDonalds. And the good thing is that parking is free even though its located in a high density area.

Since I was a young drunken teen, this Wendys has always nourished my pallet, no matter the hour. 2am? The burgers are still fresh, and the lights inside are always bright. Youll always feel welcome in this delightfully lit and heartwarming space. Try the 1.89 nachos and chili. Absolutely fantastic and always fresh
Love their 99 cent frosty and salad and baked potato combo all for $7 - always hits the spot!
GG Street Run #5 Drop 1 : 00h23 Total : 00h23 We found it even faster than Wendys CM destroys the competitors on the Internet.
My burgers were good I be back soon

The seating area is open with windows all around. It is clean and the food is great. There can be an almost 5 minute wait during lunch and dinner times, but, then you get your freshly cooked burgers or fresh fries and a Frosty to top off your meal. Where else are you going get a tasty baked potato?
The drive thru here is super fast

Sometimes they make mistakes but they always fix it quickly and get it right. The burgers are amazing. If you prefer your Burgers to be less salty then Wendys is the place. Go for the Triple Burger, you wont be disappointed. Youll probably want some extra mustard, ketchup or hot sauce on that triple Burger. And theyve got the coolest Drink Machine that Ive seen. You can pour your drink from your cell phone. Yes, thats correct.
Always s good palce for a quick burger snack
Service was great but slow due to insufficient number of staff. Food on par. Great atmosphere, quiet with multiple groups of ppl evenly spaced apart and socializing respectfully.
Good burgeres, fast service, drive thru was quick.
This Wendy s seems to be in a high traffic area. Staff worked to the bone with dedication and still providing pretty decent take out food.

Cleanest fast food and least caloric. The grilled chicken or the chili are always top notch. If youre stuck for time, as I was today, its a perfect stop. Avoid all the heavy sauces and youll be just fine. Great location and superb service.
Pretty good for a fast food joint, but the Friday afternoon crew is clearly not up to par.  Imagine getting a poutine ( which is usually great) with no fork AND frozen curds
Never disappoints, always a satisfying meal.

We visited the drive thru at Wendys on Cambie and Broadway area on 7th Ave. It is a good location for a fast food place especially there isnt any other drive thruh in that area. We got our meals very fast. I got the taco salad and my husband got a cheese burger. The fries were hot and fresh and my salad was good except I didnt get a spoon for my hot chilli, its tricky to eat it with a fork. The parking lot is old and tight with not much space to maneuvere or park comfortably to eat in your car. This Wendys is very old and it needs a face lift but we are still thankful that its there.
Burger was all hot and ready and I dined in, order was 69.

I recently worked a festival at the till (Im a bartender) and I realized how much work the people on the tills do, so I want to say they do an amazing job! And deserve so much respect, and the JBC will always be my go to classic if I need a snack at Wendys always fresh lettuce, and tomatoes which really makes a huge difference and its been consistent from when i was young until now, hasnt changed which I appreciate and goes a long way.
I really love Sushi Mugen because of delicious food
Staff is working hard to serve you better Thanks Food
Staff kills it. They deal with insane volume and all sorts of customers but their work ethic remains steadfast.
Great service awesome view

We ordered salads and drinks service was fast and efficient !! We order one diet coke with ice and one with no ice . Salads without blue cheese .. and yes they give us exactly what we want with a smile on her face .. Fast ,, friendly,, efficient!!!
Great cheeseburger, varities of own choices of Kiosk machine drinks. Fresh, burgers, fries ( fresh cut with skin on ) fries. Spacious, friendly services. ( washroom is great too ) Be back again!

detailed_reviews.reviewer_name: Miguel Ivan De los Rios Lozano
detailed_reviews.review_text: The best hamburguer ive eat in Vancouver
As always, good food and good service
There is parking available which is a great add on
Ordered door dash, all mods were met food was hot upon delivery quality chicken and beef. Fries were meh

detailed_reviews.reviewer_name: Heinstrung: Rope Access Solutions Chris Heine
detailed_reviews.review_text: They have very positive staff. I walked in as a construction worker, and was remembered when I came in next week. Extremely great customer service, something youd expect out of a small town. Definitely put a smile on my face.

If I could choose from one fast food burger chain.. Without any hesitation, itd be, the one and only, Wendys!!!! For all the years, its been around, the taste (in my opinion) hasnt changed! If anything, I believe it has gotten better in the overall taste and juiciness of each (beef) burger!! The same goes for each style, texture & spice, that goes with all of Wendys combos and single-signature sides: Salads, Fries and of course, the Frosty!!

Gotta love Wendys frosties staff are polite just dont pay to much attention to the homeless man that swears and beats up his quato contiuesly hes just a little bit touched in the head, and doesnt have the slightest clue that what he is doing is absurd. But the food is still good
Always made fresh. Worth waiting for. Parking lot is tight now that cars have gotten bigger. I like s frosty once in a while.
There service and food was great but one guy stand near the door and bagging for money.
Good juicy burger and dont forget your frosty (malt) so yummy!

I love this remnant of 1980s Vancouver. Can you imagine a time when fast food was so popular the restaurant needed 2 floors? Its a calm spacious place to hang out during non peak hours. Delicious food!
Actually one of the better Wendys Ive been too.  The food was prepared quickly, the service was friendly.  No complaints
Very great place clean and big

Hot food Daves big sandwiches I love Wendys burgers and their fries my favourite is dipping the fries inside of a chocolate frosty yum yum many things on the item good location fast service Curb Your hunger stop in and have a big burger a single double or triple choice is yours and they have fantastic chicken sandwiches yeah!
We were just in town visiting. Some people in our group did not want to try a local restaurant so a few people went here. Order was correct and the staff was nice! Would recommend.

This makes me feel things, things like regret. Its as though all the liquid in my face has been made solid and is trying desperately to escape through my pores, but it cannot. Blue flames surround me in my agony. The fries taste like nutmeg and other seasonal spices, this brings some comfort. The food here just makes me feel hungrier. I am so cold.

Wendy was very nice place to have dinner with my family .fantastic evening with chicken strip , and bake potato . Wendys gave us the opportunity to spend good moments with my family with out the hassle of cooking and washing dishes for a very good price.   . The enviroment is safe and friendly.

Recently renovated this spot has arranged its seating to take advantage of nice views of downtown against a mountain backdrop. Menu has had a nice makeover. Cheap Chilli worth the drive to their ample parking lot.
Long lines usually but always fast and fresh! Parking lot is pretty busy for 30mins stay max. Convenient location with Drive thru.

March 2019  Usually get my favourite the baconator.  Decided to try  Asiago mushroom burger combo.  Was not my favourite choice. 100% satisfaction.  Rowena, restaurant manager replied to review and as we were not pleased, generiously replaced to my satisfaction with my favourite the Baconator combo. Juicy, well prepared, bacon crisp, will continue to be a favourite destination for my burger addiction. Again parking lot full, restaurant less than 10% full, cars park on the lot and drivers go down the street to shop. Parking needs to be enforced so customers of Wendys have more spaces to park. 2018  Still one of the best burgers and my favourite over other chain burger joints.  Wife had the single cheese with Caesar salad, I had the baconator double with a Caesar salad with drinks of your own choosing. They were larger burgers fresh, juicy and tasty.  Way better than the coupon two can dine for $10.99 usually which are dry and tasteless.   Like the renovations makes the place look cleaner and roomier.  Prices still better than the burger specialty joints.  Worth a try. Parking can be a pain.  The lot is always full of cars with drivers going down the street to Home Depot or Canada Tire and at times there are no spaces available, needs better parking enforcement.

A place that have acces from any transport method sice it is near to main bus routes and subway station. Food is fresh and available order through app. Parking: Parking is avilable by the side Wheelchair accessibility: Have a ramp
Revised, They have improved in getting orders right... Older review: I love Wendys! ...Only 4 starts for this location because sometimes they get my order wrong at this location

Went through the drive thru.  One of the few drive thrus down in this area.  Great place to order a fast bite while the little one is asleep in back seat.  Service was quick and the food was great.  Leaves my stomach better feeling than eating at MCDs.

A typical Wendys, nothing too special about it. Good food, good service and very close to the Skytrain. This might be the only case of a Vancouver fast food place being too big. The dining area is never 100% clean and its possible to be out of range of the wi-fi signal if you sit one of the tables at the far end of the restaurant. It feels more like Cactus Club than a fast food place, which isnt really a bad thing.
I mainly go there for the frostys. So damn good, they are !I just love em so much. Try one, you will enjoy them, I promise.

I never go to any Wendys other than this one. Has a view of the mountains, lots of parking, friendly staff. A little hard to get into because its on the corner of a highway entrance. There is no order kiosk at this location, youll have to go to Cambie for that
We loved it here, the place was clean and the service was great and the food was perfect
To be honest I slipped in the restaurant & hurt my self really bad! Otherwise food good! Its Wendys my favorite fast food restaurants!
Newly renovated. They have amazing soda machines now.

I had to go to a appointment at cambie and Broadway  so i thought  id grab something to  take home to eat so  I stopped by Wendys I have to say  I notice how clean the restaurant was  for a fast food type restaurant  the service was  excellent the staff was very friendly and professional  out of most of the fast food restaurants ive been at in the past Wendys  definitely  gets a 5 star rating keep up the good work.

Probably one of the best Im starving and its 3am drive thrus to hit up that isnt Micky Ds. Although one thing is for certain that another post mentioned, there isnt a very friendly employee who enjoys life very much. But hey, doesnt stop me from ignoring her bullcrap and enjoying my food.

The Wendys at W. Broadway & Cambie, Vancouver, is a WELCOME reprieve from the hustle & bustle of city life. Inside, COMFORTABLE seating, GOOD food, & a RELAXING atmosphere add up to a good meal had by all. FUN drink machines!!!
JBC is very good with 2.4$.  One of the best burgers you can get considering the price point.
Thats my fav. Fast food place always has good deals but you cannot find them on mobile you have to check as old school. But they are still sooo good!!
Quick service, very nice, and staff deals with the broad range of social situations very well.
Burger s so good!

if youre looking for some hamburgers Wendys is the place at certain hours you have to wait to order cause is really busy area but even though it worth it, good service fast serving the food and accessible the parking is hard to find in weekdays, i like Wendys from 8th Ave. and Cambie all the time I have a chance come and order to eat here .
Good view of the city, nice food and clean place.
Wendys burgers are great, this place is rather big, spacious. Theyre fast, food is delicious, great stop after shopping at HomeDepot thats close by.
Service was quick with friendly staff.  Recently renovated but the parking situation is still the same,  a bit tight...  At least I didnt have to park around the block for a quick bite!

I mean, if you like one, your going to like them all really. Thats the thing about large chains. Consistancy. Consistancy is key 8n running a large successful business. Theyre frostys are the bomb diggity, no doubt.
Great Service. Quality cleanliness at the cashier. The dining area could use a little bit more TLC.
One of the best Wendys around. Free parking when eating and friendly staff. Very reasonable price too. My fav fast food place.
This Wendys has lots of space to eat from with a good amazing selection of foods
Great Food, Great Team and Great Store !!! My favorite Wendys store in Vancouver. Congratulations to all the staff !!! Every single one is doing a great job !!!
spicy chicken wasnt even that spicy
I had son of bacconater my wife had chicken. We ate inside. It was clean and quiet.
Good burgers, fries, salads, nuggets, lemonade, ice cream, and soup. Small = competitors medium and its unlimited refillable. Never regret choosing here.
Overall good go there do shopping get  food spend time with kids
Good place to go for tasty hamburgers, french fries, soda, and dessert. I sometimes go there to meet up with friends.
Wendys is by far the superior fast food chain.  Thanks for keeping your drivethru open late for all of us who work nights!
Was a quick visit justed got a coffee and some ice-cream,  servers always nice and friendly keep it up guys
Absolutely delicious and nutritious. Highly recommended. Lots of places to sit. Best spicy chicken burger ever.

detailed_reviews.review_text: Decent quality of food and service it usually pretty quick. Love their pop fountain. The clearness of the parking lot needs a little bit more work.
The food is good! The drink have so many type. Will be back soon

I am always blown away by the sheer quality of wendys both food and service. I value quality, good customer service, abd above all, a good cost to content ratio. Every time I go to mcdonalds I am utterly disappointed. This isnt an exagderation either. They leave food unwrapped in the bag leaking all over, they charge too much for ugly, poorly made sandwiches, the fill products partly full. Wendys, I really want to thank you for offering affordable options with pristine quality. You are without doubt, the best fast food restaraunt chain in Canada.
One of few remaining stand alone store in city of Vancouver.   Hamburger is the best among all fast food chains,  but I particularly like their grilled chicken Burger,  very tender and juicy
Sabrina K was the best worker at Wendys that I have ever had. So charming, lovely and polite. She cares about HER customers. solid 5/5 I highly recommend this Wendys, because of the friendly cashier.
This Wendys is great! It has a Japadog truck outside where you can get Japadogs! Its a little cramped in the restaurant, take your order out to the Infinite Tires accross the street.
The breakfast sandwich I got was hot and fresh. This place is very calming to visit in the morning because there s not much people.
It was cheap, delicious, and the staff was friendly. I sat there for about 20 minutes eating and reading, and the chairs were comfortable and quiet.
Good service. Mobile order free fries coupon was not working due to app issue, but they offered the free fries anyway.
Service and food is consistently good at this location.
This place is heads and shoulders above McDonalds. When the ingredients are fresh, it makes all the difference.

The staff of this Wendy s location are fantastic, courteous and quick, friendly and helpful.  The food is higher quality than other fast food chains, while reasonably priced.  I prefer the drive through because to it usually quicker; the food delivery drivers always go inside and make the walk-in line longer.
Wendys stepped up their game big time with the renovations. The new soda machines are amazing. Diet vanilla Barqs is perfect. Still loving the square burgers.
Jr. Bacon Cheeseburger is the best. I tried the double one and that s too greasy. You should buy two Jr. Bacon Cheeseburger.

I would reccomend bringing wet wipes because the tables arent very clean. Also, they DO NOT accept orders from people who walk into the drivethru. Order inside if you didnt bring your car. Parking: Not much parking, presumably because its a small plot of land and a drivethrough is there.
Good place to get something fast and delcious to eat.
Food always on point Kind staff Efficient Food : 4/5
Very good burgers and fresh
Good and quiet place to enjoy a good meal
The people that work here are really great at their job. Thanks
Ive seen the kind staff here deal with difficult people with class - very dignified.
The food here is simply mouthwatering.
Nice, helpful people working there. Food quality is some of the best Ive had at Wendys. Food
Love this place!  Pricing can be great.  Patty sizing are much bigger than other fast food joints as well!
Always made the way food is requested.  Thank you.
The buger patty was so juicy and delicious! It was one of my favorite fastfood places here in Vancouver. It was a quick brunch for me but I got so full I ate dinner so late.
I ve been to this store 100 s of times. Busy or quiet times. Never had a bad experience.
Its a good place to dine and they have a drive through as well

Fast and complete service. The food was hot but not too hot. Everything I purchased was in the bag. As always the frosties were thick and delicious. When they were short on my chicken strips they gave me a small order of chicken nuggets to make up for it. Id say thats excellent business. You get a chance to go by this Wendys, I suggest you do so.

Good burgers..... Love their Chili. Update: just got back from Wendys. Today they started serving their new breakfast menu. I had baconator sandwich with seasoned wedges. I can say for certain that right now, they have the best value breakfast meal in the fast food market. Loved it.

The restaurant was very clean and maintained well. I enjoyed my experience here because the staff were very helpful and very friendly. The food ofcourse are awesome and reasonably priced. The location is perfect. I highly recommend this place for anyone who loves great food, great service, great staff. I also want to mention how clean the washroom are. To me, thats extremely important because if the washrooms are clean it reflects of the quality of their staff and the management. I am 100%+ very satisfied.
Got some chicken nuggets. Fresh

For some reason this is the best Wendy s around - everything is always super fresh and hot. We always have issues with other locations, so we will go out of our way to drive here if we are wanting a quick drive-thru meal.
It was very clean and has kind Staff
This is superior to Mcdonalds. They dont cut corners. They dont charge no bag tax! Yes Vancouver there is a bag tax. Oct 15th mayoral election. Vote in a woman!

I mainly order at their drive through, never been inside. The service is good and the employees are very polite. The food is well made and taste pretty good. The time to receive my food is quite reasonable, depending on what time of day you go there of course. As well, the restaurant being placed by a busy street and other big retailers, this place will be busy during most of the day.

Its very nicely renovated which gives it an open airy feel. Big windows means you can enjoy whatever weather is outside. Staff are very nice and keep the place clean. Food is your standard Wendys food so no complaints there. Very well-run location.

Very friendly driver through lady, we got two 99cent frosties and will continue until the promo is over  . Entrance is near a corner / busy intersection; be careful pulling in. Also, take the drive through corner WIDE so avoided rubbing your nice tires and rims unlike the person infront of us

I love this Wendys with a passion. It was renovated a few years ago, and is now the most beautiful fastfood place in the area. Great clean and brightly lit joint. Their baked potatoes are on point, but lets not forget what I love most about this place... their soda machines. Any combination you can think of, they have, even in diet.

This Wendys is always quick and hot and fresh... I usually use drive through though I dont know how it is dining inside, but compared to many drive-thru places in lower mainland for some reason they got it going on correctly here

Clean friendly staff and fast never gone through the drive thru but dinning inside in the 4 or 5 visits have been pretty pleasant for me. Bathrooms are clean and tables are cleaned and looked after all in all good Wendys.
The new Wendys breakfast menu is really decent. The spiced breakfast potatoes are excellent, not even comparable to what the competition offers.

Im biased coz its Wendys. Typical fare, they still serve the fanta zero that I crave so theres that. No problems so far after ordering here in person or online. The drive thru always has a line going as well as inside so do take that into consideration. Limited seating is also in effect.

I do not like eating fast processed food. But if I have to, due to money or time constraints,  I will only eat at Wendys! They give you a good deal for your money, and the taste is much better than the other fast food restaurants.  Thanks Wendys.
Quiet, relaxing , ideal place for me to get breakfast eventhough a bit farther from me its worth the peace and quiet .
Most importantly, the fries were hot.
Convenient location and great service, though most of the time there is a long queue. Freshly made fast food. Worth a visit.

We came by on the last day of the baconator burger special for $5. Our burgers were cooked to order and delivered hot. We shared fries and a limitless soft drinks. Quite a steady stream of customers lined up. Lots of staff to bus, clean tables and empty garbage. This location is very efficient and doesnt keep their counter customers waiting while they serve their drive thru customers!! Reliable location to visit. They have a large screen tv showing CNN news to diners. Lots of seating, bright open windows make it inviting to eat in.

Staff are really good. Hard working. Friendly and fast. Food is always tasty and fresh. Great location on Marine Drive. Parking: Ample. Kid-friendliness: Good selection. Wheelchair accessibility: Auto door and street level entrance.

After landing at YVR I stopped here to eat, My burger was a little delayed, but even though I didn t complain the manager offered me a free Frosty. And the burger was freshly made. Great service, those are the things I remember.

The service was very good for fast food. It didnt even feel naughtie going there. The decor has been modernised and looks and feels really nice and the food was the best quality of Wendys Ive had. Really worth a pop by if your in the area and need a burger fix!

Super busy sometimes, other times its a ghost town. Hit or miss really. Had lunch here Sunday June 24th at 1pm and it was crazy crowded out the door. Had lunch yesterday (Sunday July 1st) at same time, and the place was empty  SCARY EMPTY lol as to their quality, they always get our order right, ive never had a complaint. Always quick an efficient and with smiles!!
I think this was my best experience with customer service at a Wendys location. The staff were super friendly and helpful. We will be going back!
Like every Wendys. Food is always good and looks presentable. Customer service is great, though orders do get mixed up sometimes when its busy.

Me and my son went for a  snack and while eating Manager Teresa came and ask how we doing and has a chat with her. She is awesome , the service is absolutely fantastic . Very good customer service . Teresa is very friendly. Good foods
My favourite restaurant. Double stack best of the best

Pros: -love the salad selection -love the chili, baked potatoes, sea salt fries (sets them apart from the other fast food joints) -the quality of the burgers (good quality beef, burgers have all the fixings, even the jr. burgers) -friendly drive thru staff Cons: -limited parking spots Overall, I would definitely choose Wendys over McDonalds any day!
Newly renovated dining room is bright and spacious, giving a more relaxed atmosphere. It even has patio seating, perfect for summer. Mixed drink dispenser provides value to your meals.
A little difficult to find the parking entrance during rush hour but aleays great drive-through and in-house service. The staff here always go out of the way to ensure your order is right.
Food is always fresh and tasty. They make the best baconator out of all the locations. Bacon is always crisp and plentiful on my burger. Love that they have the coca cola freestyle machines.
Got there 30min before closing. No problems getting any of the food I wanted to order.
The burgers, salads, chili and baked potatoes at this location have been consistently hot and fresh. Great staff and good food.

As far as corporate fast food goes, Wendys is the best, and this location specifically, offers great friendly service, very modern decor, fantastic layout and excellent parking. Call it Nostalgia or whatever, but I love Wendys.
Honestly one of the best Wendy s I ve ever been to because the staff are so dang nice ! Love coming here, I never go to the one closest to my place !
Hot   food is the best Its not too bad today Food

Like the friendly staff, order is always fast and accurate. Be patient, they have new immigrant, staff on work Visas, from different countries, training, and working here. Like the managers, always friendly.
Great service and the quality of the food is consistent regardless if it is busy or not. This is my go to place to get my fast food fix even though there are closer fast food places
Awesome fresh burger Pattys not from frozen anymore....great pop machine with 100 flavours. So much better than the old Wendys. Price was great and the new burgers were awesome.
Always great mostly because they have great service and they put veggies on the burgers.
Kept clean, staff are nice, and the parking lot is adjacent to a pokemon gym. Triple win. Oh, and the food is decent too. I mean, really, its a Wendys.
Excellent service, nice food the inly thing is right now there s no coke or other normal flavors of sodas
love the Portobello cheese burger and baked potatoe! Nothing like a FROSTY to wash it down! I recommend! Check it out!
I always love coming here as the employee are always polite and quick to get your order . I also enjoy eating in a clean environment in which these guys nail perfectly.
Food was got and delicious. Longer wait then usual but well worth it.
Really quick service during lunch hours. Never had ordered wrong. Staff is friendly
Went there in the evening, 7 ish, busy time. They have a solid team there getting everyones order right n asap.
The food is always fresh and fair. The customer service is great.
Very quick service and food was good.
This place has the good frosties that are hard and not runny. Also when you ask for a large ice water you actually get a large ice water! A+ job!!
Good, clean & friendly atmosphere, service still slow with line ups happening constantly, but much better than my previous 2 reviews.
Busy location but staff keeps it rolling at efficient speed. Busy means food is fresh and hot, which it was.
Got to love a frosty on a summer night! This restaurant is renovated and kept clean. 5 stars for this place!
better burgers then any McDonalds can make and now with there new french fries i highly recommend them for fast food goes and there quick and never have messed
I always have an exceptional experience at Wendys. Burgers are always on point. Gotta mention the spicy chicken burger which slays time and time again.
The cleanest, newest, most consistent Wendys in Vancouver. Definitely a step up from the old, tired Wendys that was in this location before the ground-up renovation that finished last year.
I go to a few different Wendys and this one consistently has great tasting food and friendly staff.
The freshness and good quality of the meat, veggis and good price. The customer service is very  good too.
Nicest Wendys I have ever been to - plus they have those awesome mix your own drink stations... diet caffiene free vanilla coke ftw.
Always great service here
Great place to visit
I love this place. Its one of my lifes guilty pleasures. Unfortunately Im probably going to die of a heart  attack from dining there more than I should
food is always delicious and theres a nice selection on the menu, better than most, and theres the baconator need. I say more
If I must go for a fast food I will do Wendys Better portions better flavours great side options

Food was awesome and super fresh! Was pleasantly surprised with their bold coffee!! Will definitely return!
Freestyle drinks here. Good service, competent staff, always gets my order right even if its complicated.
The baked potato with cheese and bacon was so good.  And the chocolate frosted are perfect for summertime.
About 250 metres from FLO Level 2 electric car recharging plugs.  Good fast food.
The young man at the counter was very patient and professional.
The drive thru service at this location is impressively quick.  The food always seems to be ready the moment you drive up to the window.

detailed_reviews.review_text: Amazing service. Delicious food. Great prices. I ve never been disappointed by a Wendy s Spicy Chicken Burger, Fries and Frosties. Frosties are always delicious, creamy and delightful. Chicken burgers are consistently warm, crispy and hearty, and the fries are always 10/10. The service here is great too! Amazing staff, friendly and such nice people!

Ordered via SKIP the dishes and the overall experience was fantastic. The food was relatively warm and fresh considering the delivery time. Hit the spot for the late night craving and I would highly recommend this to anyone. The spicy chicken sandwich is a solid choice with the sea salt fries as the combo. The classic summer frosty  completes the meal. Prepare for a food coma to follow. Not exactly fitness freak nutrition but you only live once, moderation is key! Lol

Went here for super late lunch: very good spicy chicken sandwich and perfect poutine! Service:  fast and friendly; tables and seats were clean. They were sanitizing seats and tables after guests. Will return for frosty when it s sunny out

Thank you Wendys for this incredible Caeser salad - in February no less! The grilled chicken was so juicy, the lettuce fresh and the bacon and parmesan is real. The staff in the drive thru were professional and quick. Update for June - just got the strawberry salad, like are you kidding me? This is so fresh and delicious I just cant believe it! Will definitely be back. I added a picture of my double patty burger to show the veggies - they are crisp and fresh - not easy to find in most fast food places.

I have never had a problem with my orders. May it be 1, 3, or 7 orders at one time. Never misses. Jashan is a great employee. Friendly and courteous. Every time I order,  shes there,  so I cant really say if shes not around if the place is run as smooth as when she manages.

Food was what you expect from Wendys. Manager was nice. I was a little salty that they made me go back in line since there was three minutes left in breakfast. However they already changed the menus to Lunch/Dinner but whatever. Its a little outdated Wendys but good atmosphere, no issues with other patrons and the area.
Love their coffee! Their food is not bad either and the girls behind the counter are very sweet.
They serve real food, fresh food a and offer great value.  Ms. Tamvir, Somer (manageress) are awesome.

I came here for lunch many times.   Service is always good. Staff are friendly and less crowded. Good to meet up with friends. Restaurant is spacious and ample parking.  Way much better than going to the mall.  No hesitation to come back especially when they have a coupon.  Compare with similar fast food Restaurants, Wendys is my favorite.

Wendys is a popular fast food chain that is known for its burgers, chicken sandwiches, and fries. The restaurant has a reputation for using high-quality ingredients and preparing food fresh to order, which sets it apart from some of its competitors. The menu at Wendys offers a good variety of options, including a range of burgers and sandwiches, salads, sides, and desserts. They also have a breakfast menu that is available at select locations. The prices are reasonable, and there are often deals and promotions that can make the food even more affordable.

The only fast food restaurant has baked potato. Their chilli (with beans & burger meat) is also very tasty. Their hamburger still retain some beef taste. Their senior coffee which is free for me was always freshly made. It a fast food restaurant which does not give you fast food tastes. I like going to Wendys. Always give me a good meal. Parking: Parking just outside. Minimum walking. Always find empty spots.
Made me wait 10 minutes across the window but they gave me a complimentary extra fries for the wait.  I cant complain.
Ordered large chili and fries for $1 on app. Good meal eating inside restaurant.
Tasty & clean. Drive-through service was quick.

These guys have always been fast in the drive through. They handle difficult customers well but when dining in the restaurant, but skip/Uber/door dash orders seem to take priority over in-person orders and orders take a long time to be filled.

This is the location in Burnaby on Kingsway. Super friendly staff. Greet customers on drive thru board. Always smiling. Warm greeting when leaving. Sometimes a wait but dont mind waiting a few for hot fresh food. Been visiting this location for 20 years and some of the staff have been here that long too. When its a good place to work its a good place to eat.
Wendys online app ordering is very convenient and we got lots of offers with free gifts and discounts. Still love their frostys over 10+ years. Dont change

Havent been to Wendys in a few years but decided to give it a go again.  The bacon deluxe was $4 and a delicious surprise. Tasty, juicy, fresh.  The fries were excellent too.  Went thru drive thru around 1230 and there was a wait to get the order but it was worth it.
Ive been going here awhile now and the management really listens to the customers concerns. Food is always delicious and fresh! Definitely worth it
Good food, good service,  and a pleasant environment.  My favorite burger is the Jr. bacon cheese burger.
Same place same tastes same vibes. Love it.

Customer Service is their motto and it shows, Had an issue with a drive thru order, they replaced the meal with a smile and followed up to ensure everything was good. The replacement looked just like what is advertised. You all know how rare that is.. I must say it was a great to see a place that still believes in customer service. Thank you your staff was awesome and polite, they made me feel great and you have to commend that. (Especially since I could be considered Oscar the Grouch)

Akar is amazing! My coupon didnt work and she made a way for me to leave the store feeling a value customer. She even went far and beyond to make sure i was pleased with my order. I will definitely return to this location

Ive been here several times and always found the store clean, well staffed, and providing quality service and food. Their drive thru is great but Id recommend leaving the stretch Hummer or limousine at home since its quite the turn when going through with a full parking lot. I always get a Junior Cheeseburger Deluxe since its the best value and find them always to be fresher tasting than any competitors burgers.

Good service, friendly drive through staff and food has never dissapointed. Building is a bit outdated but still spacious inside. Has a large roof window at the lower section for nice lighting in the morning/afternoon.

Great service, very good staff. Theres a night manager that makes up for his slight lack of bedside manner with crazy good order taking skills and very fast and efficient service. They have to deal with some less than desirable night time visitors and they really handle it all really well. (I work graveyard so Im normally grabbing a bite at around midnight) Ive worked in Wendys for 2 years at another location and this one runs very well!
Excellent service and a super fancy pop machine
Canadian Wendys is better than ours!!!  They still have chili cheese nachos!!!!  I miss those!!!!!
Love this place because it has good salads, Chile, and great chicken strips.  Staff is friendly and hard working.  Recommended.

I tried spicy chicken sandwich which is very fresh and so good. It would be great if they start keeping small menu on the tables. Though they are taking all the precautionary steps for covid protection for there customers.
Best fast-food burger joint you can find. Always fresh always spot on.  Their burgers have never disappointed so far.  Also love their frostys!!
I love this place! Its good to do work, meetings, and good food to keep this mortal body filled with sustenance

Wide variety of foods from excellent salads to chili to baked potatoes to hamburgers.  Plenty of seating. Nice solarium type seating in a lower level.  Friendly staff. Not as modern as some of the other Wendys but still great.

Usually visit this location after work , and it s probably the best service I have received from any other Wendy s. Jimmy is one person who stands out from the rest, he always greets customers with that smile! He s a great, hard worker, and I enjoy watching his interactions with other customers. And we always remembers me !

Nav Bhullar was so so helpful and so patient with us (we made several changes to our order and asked for many modifications as we are vegetarian). She was very kind and I would definitely come back, just because she works here.
Their burgers this time looked so perfect I had to take a photo. They looked even better than the professional photos.
Caring staff, careful, polite. Food looks good, never got an order wrong. Not like any of it matters when you are hungry as you are that you resort to Wendys
I just love Wendys

I love the kids menu and who can say no to frostys. My family of 6  can eat here for under $25 all in and the food presenation is exeptional. If we eat at the leading competitor it is easily north of $50 without coupons.

Just ordered from this place off UberEats! They forgot a few of my items and when I reordered from them and noted the mistake, they more than compensated for them! Thanks guys! Made our nights :)

This Wendys has been here forever, my mom and dad brought me here as a kid. It was a good place too eat then and its still a good place to eat
Wendys on Marine Drive was fast and the food was great..make sure you ask for fish fries. The large drinks are huge! Hahaha

I cant remember a fast food joint that is more disorganized than this Wendys location. They finally got my order right on the first time the last time I went, which should be the general expectation when one is waiting for his order, at any given point of time. And besides the mistake in giving the wrong orders, some of the right ordered burgers were lacking vegetables that were supposed to be in them. Sometimes I see customers stand around for a very long time, either waiting for their orders or waiting for someone to take their orders.  And it is never even all that overwhelmingly busy with the number of customers that come in. Lets be very clear for all of my fellow foodies out there - this restaurant is not fast food or even quick service.  This is a highly tailored, streamlined dining experience. When you enter, ask the matre-d what the chef recommends that day.  During my visit it was the Spicy Chicken Sandwich and I was informed there was a limited run based on available farm-to-table ingredients.  Boy was I lucky - it was prepared fresh by the gifted young chef, Braydon, and promptly brought to me by an extremely professional waiter Ghazal. The plating was impeccable, as if the foil was designed for my personal sandwich itself.  Absolutely to die for.  The sauce must be truffle infused because it was heavenly.  The bun was clearly artisan, I think from a local bakery on Lonsdale.  The tomato had to have been grown that day and I could ABSOLUTELY tell that the chicken used to make the sandwich was the alpha of the roost.  A prime specimen, surely. I cannot say enough positive things about this experience.  I will be returning, that is, if I am lucky enough to get in again *wink wink*!
